on embedding identity change, no migration UX (pm-wt0g)\n12. Full reindex doesn't default to stale-only (pm-o3nr)\n13. pending-refresh.json not in gc --scope embeddings (pm-3b1t)\n14. type/priority/assignee absent from semantic corpus (pm-jyie)\n15. No offline/BM25 fallback provider (pm-75k9)\n16. No persistent hybrid_semantic_weight setting (pm-2xwh)"
